name: Damaged of Buddhism
description:
This is the first roll of film that we experiment with while developing.
All equipment was brought to the outdoor of my faculty. 
The developing process was going well step by step. until the process that 
we must Swipe the water out of the film after developing is complete. 
Which to swipe the water out easily by using your finger swipe or sponge 
to make the film not scratch But we don’t know what inspired us to pick 
up “Napkins” to wipe that water out at that time. There you go. 
Damaged Buddha
